{
  "id": "adv_main_02_04_01",
  "title": "東京編1章16話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私達がレボリューションジャムに\n出演するんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to perform\nat Revolution Jam?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.27396545410156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。フェスの運営から\n月のテンペストに出演依頼が来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. We got a request from the organizers\nfor Moon Tempest to perform at the festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "これは凄いことですよ！　この音楽フェスは\nアイドルにとって憧れのイベントなんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s an amazing opportunity!\nThis music festival is the envy of all idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.23139970713648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな大イベントから出演依頼が来るなんて\n夢みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe we got a request from such a huge event…\nIt’s a dream come true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私達のパフォーマンス力と音楽性が\n高く評価された、ということでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I suppose this means they’ve recognized\nour good showmanship and musicality?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.904937247572278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……それってそんなに凄いことなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it really that amazing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.29675128870997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "凄いに決まっていますわ！\nまさかこんな大イベントを知りませんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it’s amazing!\nDon’t tell me you’ve never heard of this big event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "へー、そうなんだ\n聞いたことなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uhhh. That’s right.\nI’ve never heard of it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.11341805074406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんてことですの！\nアイドルにあるまじき発言ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what is the meaning of this?!\nThat statement is unbecoming of an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.54675138407739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "口で説明するより見てもらった方が早いな\nこれが去年のフェスの写真だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead of explaining it‚ I think it would be faster to just show you.\nThese are photos from last year’s festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5980.08471741069,
          "startTime": 52.44675138407736
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　凄いお客さんの数だねー！\nこれって何千人くらい入ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! That’s a huge audience!\nHow many thousands does that space fit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5800847174107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "桁が違いますよ\nメインステージは数万人を収容出来るんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re missing a zero!\nThe main stage fits tens of thousands.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.51341805074405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "まん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tens of thousands?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.18008471741072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストにはこのメインステージで歌って欲しいそうだ\nこれは大抜擢だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And they want Moon Tempest to perform on the main stage.\nThis will be great PR.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "それはとても光栄なお話ですけど……\n私達にそんな大役が務まるでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s an honor for us to receive this offer…\nBut can we really handle such a big role?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "何を弱気になってるの。今までだって\nどんな困難も乗り越えて来たじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why the lack of confidence? We’ve overcome\nall kinds of obstacles to get where we are today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.06666666840513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、最近なんか調子いいし\n今ならなんでもやれる気がするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei has been in good form lately.\nI feel like I could do anything right now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "その通りですわ！\n勢いに乗った私達に出来ないことなどありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Exactly!\nNow that we have momentum‚ there’s nothing we can’t accomplish!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこの仕事、やります。やらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nWe accept the offer. Please let us take it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 500,
          "startTime": 102.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "あら。あれは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. Is that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 106.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 106.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、レッスンお疲れ様\n全員で居残り練習か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job at your lesson‚ everyone.\nAre you all staying behind to practice on your own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、フェス用の新しい振り付けを練習中なんですが\n難易度が高くてみんな苦戦していて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We’re still memorizing the new choreography for the festival.\nIt’s really difficult‚ so we’re struggling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けのことはダンスコーチから聞いたよ\nもし間に合いそうにないならレベルを下げても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard about the choreography from your dance coach.\nIf you can’t perfect it on time‚ you could lower the difficulty…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、レベルは落としたくありません\n私達に出来る最高のパフォーマンスで臨みたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. We don’t want to lower the difficulty.\nWe want to give the best performance we possibly can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "心配ならご無用です\n本番までには完璧にマスターして差し上げますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No need to worry.\nWe shall perfectly master the choreography by the time we’re on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.666666666674,
          "startTime": 141
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか\n完璧を目指すのもいいけど、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?\nAiming for perfection is admirable‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ああーーーーっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "び、びっくりした……\nいきなりどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
